{"tid":551420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"O記男警為探還柙女友人   涉偽造警察便箋被捕","createTime":"2018-02-05T15:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T03:02:21.000Z","uid":48093,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fe79228dd694b8cb291810b45c2ec82a71e50254","tid":551420,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180205/large/1517844819_8b60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180205%2Flarge%2F1517844819_8b60.jpg&h=af0e3b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名41歲姓張男警務人員涉嫌於去年1月至本月期間，多次向一個政府部門發送偽冒的警察便箋，以探訪一名還押犯人。警方商業罪案調查科人員經深入調查後，今午把他拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，被捕男警為有組織罪案及三合會調查科(O記)的高級警員，他涉嫌使用虛假文書及公職人員行為失當，現正被扣留調查。據知他欲探訪還柙的女友人，但因懲教署對探訪還柙人士有次數限制，故有人偽冒警察便箋。<br />\n<br />\n警方強調，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"948938436dea40d9334b9c82c39292e1d05578c2","tid":551420,"uid":62599,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"警方強調，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91539537e42ffae4110056267ab29c9728d44f0a","tid":551420,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"拉返班柳記話阻狗辦公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d651b5e8383afc6fc7ea142836eb89152c1bfca","tid":551420,"uid":2545,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"948938436dea40d9334b9c82c39292e1d05578c2","tid":551420,"uid":62599,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"警方強調，非常重視人員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:50:26.000Z","msg":"大SIR不如索性幫呢段野錄定音<br />\n一年應該可以講番百零二百次"},{"pid":"6fb6f8e913064e5c3ca4a79f9a980f87b5e14f46","tid":551420,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:50:31.000Z","msg":"當班警GOAL"},{"pid":"05fb03bebe4e6278629e78d40aafc871b659a9ff","tid":551420,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T15:58:24.000Z","msg":"阿蛇『做』文件唔駛你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f1f53c73903d4d48f7094efb6f8e9aab0fffad","tid":551420,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"入返球都無咁傷"},{"pid":"c5f27ef52c5e879a99145e055d4f680ffd80225e","tid":551420,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"呀蛇做野，行開行開！"},{"pid":"f88853958d5e5f82d0220a83a78b1404ecd5ac47","tid":551420,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"一分"},{"pid":"b55445de3856e583a4b350dbcd624f08bb076aec","tid":551420,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"O記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b442c3ad1bcd4f4a78c3e7c22e8e59a13ab2f7","tid":551420,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"阿sir犯法使唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d394d2102b07b0c3818c499a9dc0813e3d520d","tid":551420,"uid":81756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T17:39:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9152e0b4ec038c3642f5b5269870681f6dd1fa37","tid":551420,"uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-02-2018/k125VP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%